{"tid":1552774,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我都唔明點解今日要有人話前線","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T12:06:15.000Z","uid":292730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7570773f019ac4281f2ae16ca4a7e740f9f40032","tid":1552774,"uid":292730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"有份鬧前線既問下自己今日係咪繼續做冷氣點解唔出黎<br />\n<br />\n遊行去美領，吉正政府死穴驚到星期五六已經收哂手一粒TG都冇放過<br />\n比你行又唔係，唔比你行仲衰，放TG更係直線助攻，差佬出埋NoNo幾乎已經冇代價<br />\n政府可以做既就只有亂拉人，搵餓底搞亂你地<br />\n<br />\n而家已經變左亂封站亂打人，唔好話勇武和非，頭先係置地連普通市民都嚇親<br />\n係屋企睇得出政府要出牌Spin開，咪即刻諗計點救做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實你地好重要<br />\n現場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前</span><span style=\"color: green;\">中</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">後</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">全排</span></strong>4G都一樣係收得極差，開得手機睇都係要知<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>重要資訊</strong></span><br />\n一係睇有冇Breaking，一係睇文字live，一係睇逃走路線，冇時間慢慢碌人多已經load唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冷氣Post既<span style=\"color: gold;\">含金量</span>唔夠呀</span></strong></span><br />\n冷氣其實好重要：有上帝視角，又可以推Post上熱門，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">正正彌補左現場唔夠資訊既重要</span></strong><br />\n事實係好多和理非都冇入TG Group，識上連登都已好好<br />\n現場要轉陣，要散水，熱門Post提供路線好重要。<br />\n真正軍師係比具體command而唔係齋鬧鬧鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冷氣既工作好重要</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1. 資料整合/Fact Checking（逃走路線）<br />\n2. 對抗政俯帶風向（第一時間文宣，幫手執下圖推fb, twitter，兵貴神速）<br />\n3. 不分化 （當自己友「又做錯野」先唔亂陣腳，諗點救）<br />\n4. 唔亂推Post/沉Post （包括對抗自己友分化）</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">和</span><span style=\"color: red;\">勇</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">軍</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5417ae5359a29653e261d1c9134e77c697f4c637","tid":1552774,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 <br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"}]}